<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Bankview </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A master-planned neighborhood, the community in Bankview is surrounded by a breathtaking
                landscape that offers panoramic views of the Rockies.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Being one of the oldest communities in the entire city, the Bankview Real Estate offers a
                plethora of housing options ranging from vintage bungalows to high-density apartments and newly
                developed condominiums. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Bankview are regularly listed at an average price of around $670,000,
                with the available residential properties being as cheap as $195,000 and as pricey as $970,000. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Recreational opportunities abound in the area with numerous parks and playgrounds dotting
                the entire neighborhood.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Also, given its prime location, Bankview is just minutes away from the city center as well
                as a number
                of shopping complexes.</p>


        </div>
